<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <%- include("partials/_head")%>
    <script src="/scripts/contact-seller.js"></script>

    <title>GETr</title>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include("partials/_navbar") %>
    <main class="main-container">
      <div id="contact-seller-form">
        <form action="">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="exampleFormControlTextarea1">Contact Seller</label>
            <textarea class="form-control" id="contact-message" rows="4" required></textarea>
          </div>
          <div id="check-button">
            <div class="form-check">
              <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="" id="defaultCheck1" required>
              <label class="form-check-label" for="defaultCheck1">
                I agree for seller to have access to my e-mail.
              </label>
            </div>
            <button type="submit">Send</button>
          </div>

        </form>

      </div>



      <div class="listing">
        <div class="listing-image">
          <img src="/images/start.jpeg">
        </div>
        <div class="listing-right">
          <div class="listing-info">
            <div class="listing-mid">
              <div class="listing-specs">
                <h1 id="listing-brand">Fender</h1>
                <h2 id="listing-model">Stratocaster</h2>
              </div>
              <p id="listing-price">
                $829.99
              </p>
            </div>
            <p id="listing-description">
              Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical
              Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at
              Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a
              Lorem Ipsum passage
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="listing-footer">
            <button id="fave-listing" href="">Add to Favourites
              <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
            </button>
            <button onclick="contact()" id="contact-seller" href="">Contact Seller
              <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </main>
</body>

</html>
